# ğŸš€ SaaS Landing Page Generator

A full-stack web application that generates modern, responsive SaaS landing pages based on user input.

Users provide:

- Startup Name
- Industry
- Primary Brand Color
- Tone (Professional, Bold, Playful, Futuristic)

The system dynamically generates a production-ready HTML landing page styled with TailwindCSS.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- Dynamic landing page generation
- Tone-based headline & subtext logic
- Clean TailwindCSS styling
- Full HTML output
- Opens generated page in a new tab
- Modular backend template system
- Scalable architecture for AI integration

---

## ğŸ›  Tech Stack

### Frontend
- HTML5
- TailwindCSS (CDN)
- Vanilla JavaScript

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- CORS

