---

## ğŸ§  How It Works

1. User fills the form in `index.html`  
2. Frontend sends a POST request to `/generate`  
3. Backend receives input  
4. `generator.js` builds dynamic HTML template  
5. Server returns generated HTML  
6. Browser opens the generated landing page in a new tab

---

## ğŸ¨ Customization

You can modify:

- Landing page layout â†’ `/templates/generator.js`  
- UI styling â†’ `/public/style.css`  
- Form structure â†’ `/public/index.html`  
- Copy logic â†’ Inside `generateTemplate()` function  

